= Hashed Attributes

class Person
  hashed_attributes :preferences, :theme, :plan, :favorite_color
end

Person.new
#<Person:0x102c61918> {
             :id => nil,
           :name => nil,
    :preferences => {},
         :emails => nil,
     :created_at => nil,
     :updated_at => nil
}

Will let you get and set theme, privacy, plan and favorite_color through the preferences hash
